        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The twin serrated blades of this legendary rhoka sword are dull black and constantly drip with blood. Life's Last Breath is said to have been forged centuries ago for an unknown urdefhan general and has since fallen into the hands of countless other powerful urdefhan warlords.</p>\n<p>Life's Last Breath is a +3 greater striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Unholy]{Unholy} @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Wounding]{Wounding} rhoka sword with the following special abilities.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">R</span> command</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You successfully Strike a creature with <em>Life's Last Breath</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast a 9th-level <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Paralyze]{Paralyze}</em> spell on the target.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">R</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per 10 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You successfully Strike a creature with <em>Life's Last Breath</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The target must succeed at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:38] or take [[/r 4d6]] negative damage; you gain an equal amount of temporary Hit Points that last 1 minute.</p>"
